# Rasm Navigation

Use tools over memory. Parallelize discovery reads.

## Discovery ladder

1. `fd -H .` — locate files by name
2. `rg -n --hidden --glob '!.git' --glob '!node_modules' "<pattern>" <path>` — exact references
3. `pnpm exec ast-grep run --pattern "<structural-pattern>" <path>` — symbol-aware edits
4. Nx topology (`nx graph`, affected commands) before repo-wide scans
5. Read minimal slices; read a file fully before editing

